def: Membership card for the Friends of Eon, an Irish Transgender organisation established in the mid 1970s. Members from all over Ireland and included transexuals, those who were transitioning and transvestites. The Friends of Eon ran a weekly transgender club, Lola's, on Thursday nights in the Parliament Inn in Dublin from 1977-mid 1980s.
en: Membership card for the Friends of Eon, an Irish Transgender organisation established in the mid 1970s. Members from all over Ireland and included transexuals, those who were transitioning and transvestites. The Friends of Eon ran a weekly transgender club, Lola's, on Thursday nights in the Parliament Inn in Dublin from 1977-mid 1980s.
